---
title: Herby Dory Fish & Parsley Butter Sauce with Zesty Potato Chunks & Tartare Sauce
description: Tender pan-seared fish never fails to satisfy! It has all the familiar tastes of home cooking at its finest, plus a buttery parsley
sauce and a side of easy roast potatoes which make up the perfect accompaniments to this tasty dinner.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
